				<td colspan="2"><span>Mostly it is just a toy.  But there are a couple times it is kinda nice to have.
<br />

<br />
Use it all the time on PoJ trials.  Have enough mana to cast it 4+ times.  Using this to get initial aggro with AoE slow/dot will keep the other three mobs that the rest of the group are not tanking on you.  No need really to mezz just make sure you keep everything on you and you can focus on helping dps instead.   
<br />

<br />
AoE groups like a burrower raid.  No need to fade so just dump all your mana into this.  (kinda fun to actually feel like you are doing damage)
<br />

<br />
Note Ten:  You are thinking of a different song (bellow single target 222 base, 5 min. recast).  Nothing has an effect on damage on this one exect for JF (555 - 565?) x 4.  Hehe guess they didn't want us hitting things for 2k x 4 (without crits) with 3 second casting time multiple times in a row <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />.</span></td>
